{"tid":426422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又一個死傻仔比人呃錢","createTime":"2017-10-06T14:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T18:08:52.000Z","uid":46983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42d0f1acefcb3de443f9291bad371190df965281","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"嗰個傻仔就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件事係咁 我網上cut有線之後冇收過書面通知要還機 過左30日之後 佢就俾封咁嘅嘢我 如果我上去有線到還完機之後係咪都要比返罰款<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/225805_92c4c79de94b643be4d490e50b242efb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F225805_92c4c79de94b643be4d490e50b242efb.jpg&h=3f8652d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce9434da1568913f7f0f7680ad83885093de9f72","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ab9c50416afe78f63d1d51e57d7a06fefdf180","tid":426422,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"唔好交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b005a3a7231251e7b8aa79257184b01a6347f93f","tid":426422,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"乜原來仲有人用有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4d616ca0f25d1452eebc3b2f17f85130960280","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔交會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a25a2bae3c15f97ed4944fd47ed515290f709e3","tid":426422,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"成功例子:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20140922/52928720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20140922%2F52928720&d=VnsuB8eOcPj9jOy02Rsrz4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7f616d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20140922%2F52928720&h=2bf3465d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20140922/52928720</a>"},{"pid":"6b2a8630f78187c8af4745d83a2261328eef70b4","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜原來仲有人用有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一完約即走 估唔到咁都比佢陰鳩我"},{"pid":"dc1418b4d8d6d083c26c45b43f8aad729cc0a9ea","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功例子:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20140922/52928720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20140922%2F52928720&d=VnsuB8eOcPj9jOy02Rsrz4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7f616d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20140922%2F52928720&h=2bf3465d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20140922/52928720</a></blockquote><br />\n唔想出名 跪求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82eb2ca3666acd525997592c2a7d40159c32f1df","tid":426422,"uid":54736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"根本都cut唔撚到，我揸住個電話 9聽咗半個鍾頭音樂 耳都熱9埋，轉頭仲cut撚埋線，慶撚到我屎都急埋 即刻打去申請熱線揾人祭旗，第一個係女仔聽.. 算撚數....見你係女仔唔屌你.... 我收綫<br />\n<br />\n再打係條o靚仔聽，我心唸你大撚獲 初頭我好好語氣問佢係邊位....丫.... 佢又問撚番我係邊位，佢死都唔撚講自己個名， 如是者玩能咗成分鍾你係邊位 我d粗口開始忍唔撚住，屌咗佢兩撚，最後佢同我講佢姓鄧無英文名 ....算撚數.....我同佢講話cut有線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢話呢度cut唔到轉介去第2度，根住我同佢講你邊能度都唔駛轉介 我唔能想再聽你d音樂，根住佢就同我講&quot;咁我幫唔到你喇，你自己唸辦法啦&quot; 我聽能完呢句之後，我成個人個靈魂好似離能開個身體咁 d火直頭可以煲能瀉一壺水，果一刻我直頭當個能樣係妓女狂吊 當我吊得佢拍拍聲既期間，佢同我講叫我尊重下自己<br />\n<br />\n我火都嚟能埋，我同佢講我屋又搬9咗，條線仲係人屋企，你又唔能比我cut 你有無能尊重過我呀，根住佢話如果你再係咁你信唔信我cut你線 根住我同佢講&quot;你又試能下cut&quot;.....丫.....點能知佢真係cut能咗我線 嘩....我簡能值想衝入厨房立把老牛去有線切9? 我吊佢老.母...佢真係夠胆識呀!!!!<br />\n<br />\n搞到我自己都唔知自己想點，office hour又去唔到cut，我收工去佢office仲落能埋閘，我就 9揸能住個解碼器周街行，一陣間大能頭蝦整唔見埋就真係含能都無味，我都試過寄掛號，又寫信再Fax，佢就當能咗我麻瘋佬咁啋我都 ，聽日我就揸能住個解碼器上天台自殺，等d所謂區議員關注吓<br />\n<br />\n我平時返工都唔帶公事包，兩手空空幾能嘆呀，就係為能咗呢舊解碼器攪能到我日日袋住佢係公事包返工，我唸住睇下幾時可以行開一陣閃上去有線度cut，不過真係忙到抽筋行唔開，如事者我就揸住佢日日返工放工、happy hour、睇戲食飯，總之佢在我在，佢亡我亡，真係好能似一個傻仔，日日袋9住都唔知為乜，一來舊野已經重二來真係驚自已大頭蝦整唔能見，比人執到都當垃圾&rdquo;DUM &rdquo; 9咗，到時連個公事包都蝕9埋我就真係要攞日大假去遊行。<br />\n<br />\n起初d同事仲以為我買咗部新 NOTEBOOK，我都唔能識點答佢地，求能其笑吓就算，費事比佢地見到我有舊咁既野係袋以為我痴9咗線。不過我知道紙係包唔住火，有一日成班同事去飲茶，當埋單之際，我唸住係個公事包攞個銀包出嚟，點知我攞9錯咗，潛能咗個remote出嚟當銀包，我果刻真係唔能知可以講乜好，成間酒樓好似靜晒，d茶客仲以為我想轉台&hellip;..就係咁我一手揸住個remote，一手揸住個銀包埋單&hellip;&hellip;..丫&hellip;&hellip;果條酒樓亞姐重能好意思問9我個搖控係咪佢地，我面都紅能埋同佢講我袋入面仲有舊解碼器連插蘇你要唔要呀。"},{"pid":"8b5150aa1b6032dfd1c67e0ee4ead828e7407148","tid":426422,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"果陣係專登叫人上黎收<br />\n因為佢回收中心太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eb760d96e7b70cf6204404e4fbb1aebc4ce92c","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣係專登叫人上黎收<br />\n因為佢回收中心太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇過限期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我去還唔緊要 錢先緊要<br />\n唔想比狗賺"},{"pid":"5ab6ab872646eb806540cac998496f0dca28ccee","tid":426422,"uid":141496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"成功cut左 到期前三個月 已經做足準備 send信上去"},{"pid":"dd63cb0e686682e862573cc9e9d6d378895fe658","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功cut左 到期前三個月 已經做足準備 send信上去</blockquote><br />\n我都已經提前上網cut 係蠢在唔知點處理部機"},{"pid":"706f2afd7e7167242b6f653d5c4581d3b3509a4a","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd00ecad2e025bc4e1870c713ec38de424da974","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f807d17a43bc87c9ce272b51782b7e2b5049d059","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e1cb8837a91f724c6c1f711d93f552903da61a","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596864bdb6866c82a82335e671bbcb4a336182b4","tid":426422,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"留名等睇無限fax機圖"},{"pid":"15e55f3ddea04f0303576ad35ca72b440c96e119","tid":426422,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9fb616dcc9f53775